      "bullets": [
        "\"Pardon MIE?\" investigates the security architecture of Microsoft Ingestion Engine (MIE) and its associated cloud deployment permissions.",
        "Researchers highlight vulnerabilities in Managed Identity permissions where MIE can be abused to escalate privileges or access sensitive data stores.",
        "Engineers should audit Azure Managed Identity roles, restricting excessive permissions granted to automated integration and ingestion engines."
      ]
    },
    {
