      "bullets": [
        "Deploy Action Runner Controller (ARC) on Kubernetes to enable autoscaling ephemeral runners, ensuring isolated and clean build environments.",
        "Secure runners by utilizing rootless Docker-in-Docker (DinD) or Kaniko, and enforce least-privilege access using GitHub's OIDC trust federation.",
        "Reduce build latency by mounting persistent volume claims (PVCs) for dependency caching and hosting a local registry mirror."
      ]
    },
